ot. On on.<\/p>\n<p>When: Saturday, January 30\u00a0at 3 PM<br \/>\nWhere:\u00a0TBA<br \/>\nHow much: $7 if you&#8217;re experienced, and a mere nothing if this is your first hash trail<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>&lt;OK, it&#8217;s supposed to be 54 degrees and mostly sunny on Saturday for the Antarctica hash, so what was supposed to be a miserably cold late-January slog might end up to be a pleasant mild walk in the park (literally). &hellip; <a href=\"http:\/\/www.bfh3.com\/?p=2444\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&rarr;<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[7],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.bfh3.com\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2444"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.bfh3.com\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.bfh3.com\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.bfh3.com\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.bfh3.com\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fcomments&post=2444"}],"version-history":[{"count":6,"href":"http:\/\/www.bfh3.com\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2444\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2451,"href":"http:\/\/www.bfh3.com\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2444\/revisions\/2451"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.bfh3.com\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fmedia&parent=2444"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.bfh3.com\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fcategories&post=2444"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.bfh3.com\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Ftags&post=2444"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}